Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.76,0:00:06.90,Default,Robo,0,0,0,,Another new light is born.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.27,0:00:17.67,Default,Robo,0,0,0,,A long time ago, or perhaps in the distant future,\NI was in a different world.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.55,0:00:20.69,Default,Robo,0,0,0,,I still retain the memory that I was once there. {ep10}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.37,0:00:25.04,Default,Girl,0,0,0,,What was that world like?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.14,0:00:30.05,Default,Girl,0,0,0,,Was it more beautiful than here?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.78,0:00:31.76,Default,Rob,0,0,0,,I'm sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.26,0:00:36.50,Default,Girl,0,0,0,,Were there lots of things that kept each day interesting?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.24,0:00:39.04,Default,Rob,0,0,0,,I think.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.81,0:00:43.56,Default,Girl,0,0,0,,It wasn't lonely like here?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.82,0:00:53.49,Default,Rob,0,0,0,,The girl who spent her time alone in this world that had ended.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.14,0:01:00.48,Default,Rob,0,0,0,,Because I knew this place of nothingness was not fun and was a lonely place to live.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.28,0:01:03.24,Default,Rob,0,0,0,,That must be why I chose to be born here.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.43,0:01:06.73,Default,Girl,0,0,0,,Hey, did you…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.73,0:01:10.63,Default,Girl,0,0,0,,…wish to be born in a world like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.40,0:03:02.14,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Just lend the name?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.14,0:03:03.82,Sun,Sun,0,0,0,,All she needs is the numbers, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.82,0:03:07.63,Sun,Sun,0,0,0,,I'm not interested in acting,\Nbut I don't mind if it's just lending the name.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.63,0:03:10.33,Sun,Sun,0,0,0,,I bet Nagisa-chan will be thanking me.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.33,0:03:12.71,Sun,Sun,0,0,0,,And one day, the gratitude will develop into love.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.02,0:03:16.71,Sun,Sun,0,0,0,,Nagisa-chan! I have good news for you!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.71,0:03:21.12,Kyo,Kyo,0,0,0,,Tomoya, we've decided to lend our names to the drama club.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.97,0:03:29.30,Kyo,Kyo,0,0,0,,To be honest, we're not interested in acting, so it's just to reach the amount required.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.62,0:03:31.36,Ryo,Ryo,0,0,0,,This makes four members.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.36,0:03:34.37,Ryo,Ryo,0,0,0,,Enough for the student council to recognize us.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.37,0:03:39.85,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,To be honest, I feel bad,\Nsince it feels like we're tricking them.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.85,0:03:41.39,Kyo,Kyo,0,0,0,,You're too honest!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.39,0:03:43.72,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Everyone's willing to help you,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.72,0:03:45.70,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,so don't waste their thoughts, Nagisa.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.70,0:03:49.33,Kyo,Kyo,0,0,0,,Now that it's decided, let's take action!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.33,0:03:50.87,Kyo,Kyo,0,0,0,,Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.87,0:03:53.37,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,You have to act tough, Nagisa.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.87,0:03:52.12,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,Yes…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.12,0:03:53.92,Kyo,Kyo,0,0,0,,You get moving, too, Tomoya.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.92,0:03:54.75,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Yes, ma'am.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.50,0:04:00.17,Titles,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,0)\pos(957.273,411.75)}Episode 15
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.50,0:04:00.17,Titles,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,0)\pos(965.455,724.5)}A Problematic Matter
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.17,0:04:04.48,Default,Kou,0,0,0,,Oh, so you want to restart the drama club?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.48,0:04:07.30,Kyo,Kyo,0,0,0,,Yes. We want to take part in the School Festival.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.30,0:04:08.79,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,We've got the number required.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.79,0:04:13.02,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,All we need now is an advisor\Nfor the student council to recognize us.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.02,0:04:16.46,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,Could you please be our advisor?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.64,0:04:23.37,Default,Kou,0,0,0,,Could you go discuss this\Nwith a junior named Nishina Rie?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.73,0:04:25.48,Ryo,Ryo,0,0,0,,Nishina Rie-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.48,0:04:28.72,Kot,Kot,0,0,0,,As in the Nishina-san who lent me the violin?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.24,0:04:33.49,Default,Nis,0,0,0,,Ichinose-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.95,0:04:39.43,Kot,Kot,0,0,0,,Nishina-san, hello.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.75,0:04:42.51,Default,Nis,0,0,0,,It's been a while. What brings you here today?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.51,0:04:43.96,Kot,Kot,0,0,0,,It's not me today.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.29,0:04:46.93,Kot,Kot,0,0,0,,Nagisa-chan wants to talk to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.24,0:04:50.39,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,I'm Furukawa Nagisa from 3-B.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.39,0:04:54.29,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,I'm not entirely certain of the situation, but…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.89,0:04:58.48,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,Um, may I speak with her alone?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.89,0:05:03.95,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,I don't think it's very comfortable for them to see a group of upperclassmen come by.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.90,0:05:18.16,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,How did it go, Nagisa?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.02,0:05:20.42,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,Well…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.42,0:05:22.42,Default,Girl,0,0,0,,What are you going to do, Rie-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.79,0:05:27.92,Default,Girl,0,0,0,,We approached Koumura-sensei first, so we don't have to step aside.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.30,0:05:32.18,Default,Nis,0,0,0,,But Koumura-sensei was an advisor for the drama club originally,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.18,0:05:36.74,Default,Nis,0,0,0,,and they only have this year left to them.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.74,0:05:40.31,Default,Girl,0,0,0,,Are you sure?! You might not\Nbe able to form the choir club!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.31,0:05:42.94,Default,Girl,0,0,0,,You can't give up singing!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.42,0:05:48.01,Default,Nis,0,0,0,,That's why we should be thinking of what we can do for all of us to be happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.01,0:05:48.63,Default,Nis,0,0,0,,Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.77,0:05:52.11,Kot,Kot,0,0,0,,Choir club?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.11,0:05:59.23,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,Yes. They want to form a choir club\Nand asked Koumura-sensei to be their advisor.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.23,0:06:03.54,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Wouldn't the music teacher usually be the advisor for the choir club?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.54,0:06:08.98,Ryo,Ryo,0,0,0,,The music teacher already has her hands full with the wind ensemble.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.98,0:06:12.95,Ryo,Ryo,0,0,0,,The only teacher who is not advising any club is Koumura-sensei.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.95,0:06:15.54,Kyo,Kyo,0,0,0,,So, what are you going to do, Nagisa? {ep 14}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.54,0:06:18.36,Kyo,Kyo,0,0,0,,You're not going to back down now, are you? {ep 14}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.53,0:06:22.81,Default,Mis,0,0,0,,Is Sunohara here?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.15,0:06:26.08,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,No, he's not back yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.69,0:06:28.74,Default,Mis,0,0,0,,He has a call from his little sister.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.74,0:06:31.86,Default,Mis,0,0,0,,Can you take the message from her instead?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.23,0:06:35.39,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Oh yeah, he has a sister, doesn't he?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.39,0:06:37.65,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Since it's his sister we're talking about, I bet she's like….
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.95,0:06:39.66,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,“It's me, Onii-chan.”
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.29,0:06:43.93,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,…that; a very demonic girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.93,0:06:45.92,Default,Mis,0,0,0,,Could you not scare my cat please?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.12,0:06:50.33,Default,Mei,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.33,0:06:52.67,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Looks like I can greet her normally.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.30,0:06:55.64,Default,Mei,0,0,0,,Hello? Is that you, Onii-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.64,0:07:01.12,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Yes. Your brother, Sunohara Youhei, the greatest failure in life, is speaking.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.12,0:07:02.58,Default,Mei,0,0,0,,What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.99,0:07:04.69,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,She didn't fall for it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.17,0:07:09.28,Default,Mei,0,0,0,,You know, Onii-chan, I'm planning to visit you the day after tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.28,0:07:12.85,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Sorry, my sister. Right now, I'm actually behind bars.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.85,0:07:14.58,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,I got caught doing something stupid.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.58,0:07:16.55,Default,Mei,0,0,0,,There you go again, trying to change the subject.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.55,0:07:18.43,Default,Mei,0,0,0,,I'll be there no matter what you say.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.43,0:07:19.93,Default,Mei,0,0,0,,What do you want me to bring you?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.93,0:07:20.72,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,A clay doll.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.12,0:07:22.83,Default,Mei,0,0,0,,You want something like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.83,0:07:24.05,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Yes, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.99,0:07:27.57,Default,Mei,0,0,0,,If you say so, then I'll bring it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.57,0:07:29.34,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,You still can't tell?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.34,0:07:31.50,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,I'm not your brother, but—
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.52,0:07:33.12,Default-alt,Mei,0,0,0,,Oh, Mom's calling, so I'm hanging up now.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.27,0:07:34.71,Default-alt,Mei,0,0,0,,See you day after tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.71,0:07:36.08,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Hey! Hello!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.19,0:07:38.16,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Crap.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.95,0:07:40.32,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Oh well.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.85,0:07:47.36,Sun,Sun,0,0,0,,You're all so mean, forgetting about me and going home.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.36,0:07:50.32,Sun,Sun,0,0,0,,When I came to, the classroom was pitch dark.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.32,0:07:54.04,Sun,Sun,0,0,0,,I was hungry, too, and the gate was closed when I tried to go home.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.46,0:07:56.55,Sun,Sun,0,0,0,,Hey, are you listening, Okazaki?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.02,0:08:01.95,Sun,Sun,0,0,0,,Nagisa-chan, what are you reading?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.66,0:08:04.69,Sun,Sun,0,0,0,,Could it be a love letter?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.16,0:08:06.55,Sun,Sun,0,0,0,,Let's see…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.33,0:08:11.59,Sun,Sun,0,0,0,,“Give up on making the drama club. Otherwise you'll be in pain.”
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.59,0:08:12.90,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,A threatening note?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.78,0:08:20.36,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,It was inside my desk when I came back after PE.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.36,0:08:21.75,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,Who could have…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.75,0:08:26.30,Sun,Sun,0,0,0,,If you're in a fight over an advisor with the choir club, then it has to be them.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.61,0:08:30.31,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,There's no proof, so we can't say that!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.31,0:08:31.57,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,She…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.93,0:08:34.32,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,They wouldn't do such a thing!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.32,0:08:37.07,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,They're trying to sing together!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.07,0:08:39.27,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,So they would never do such a thing!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.56,0:08:45.83,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,Nishina-san was so kind to Kotomi-chan, as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.85,0:08:48.57,Sun,Sun,0,0,0,,Can you be so sure?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.38,0:08:51.04,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Where are you going?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.04,0:08:52.83,Sun,Sun,0,0,0,,I'll look into this my way.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.83,0:08:56.04,Sun,Sun,0,0,0,,I think I can report the result by the time school ends, so look forward to it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.44,0:08:57.72,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Hey, wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.72,0:09:00.23,Sun,Sun,0,0,0,,Don't worry, I won't do anything rough.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.23,0:09:02.31,Sun,Sun,0,0,0,,After all, I'm kind to girls.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.33,0:09:08.73,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,Okazaki-san, do you think it's something that Nishina-san and her friends did?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.34,0:09:14.57,Sun,Sun,0,0,0,,It really was one of the choir members.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.57,0:09:16.17,Sun,Sun,0,0,0,,A girl named Sugisaka.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.17,0:09:17.72,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Do you have proof?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.72,0:09:23.82,Sun,Sun,0,0,0,,Her classmate saw her go into a senior class\Nand put something inside a desk.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.82,0:09:25.58,Sun,Sun,0,0,0,,I'm not making this up, just so you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.16,0:09:29.54,Sun,Sun,0,0,0,,Ah, here she is.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.79,0:09:32.63,Sun,Sun,0,0,0,,I called her out.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.96,0:09:36.01,Sun,Sun,0,0,0,,Good, you came alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.53,0:09:39.69,Default,Sug,0,0,0,,The letter was something I did by myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.13,0:09:42.12,Default,Sug,0,0,0,,It has nothing to do with the other two.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.12,0:09:44.01,Default,Sug,0,0,0,,I'm the only one who did something wrong!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.01,0:09:47.06,Sun,Sun,0,0,0,,Do you think that even matters?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.06,0:09:51.06,Sun,Sun,0,0,0,,Everyone isn't thinking enough, and it's making me sick.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.06,0:09:52.23,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Hold up, Sunohara.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.23,0:09:54.43,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,Please wait, Sunohara-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.68,0:10:00.45,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,We met in the music room yesterday, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.45,0:10:02.37,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,Let's talk properly.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.83,0:10:12.65,Default,Sug,0,0,0,,Nishina-san played the violin when she was little and won many prizes at various competitions.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.68,0:10:18.36,Default,Sug,0,0,0,,Her talent was acknowledged by many people,\Nand she was supposed to go study abroad, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.01,0:10:21.35,Default,Sug,0,0,0,,But right before that was about to become a reality…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.89,0:10:24.51,Default,Sug,0,0,0,,…she got in an accident.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.22,0:10:27.16,Default,Sug,0,0,0,,Her grip became weak.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.35,0:10:33.26,Default,Sug,0,0,0,,She couldn't play the violin as well as she used to, either,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.55,0:10:38.45,Default,Sug,0,0,0,,so she enrolled in this school,\Nbut she looked lonely all the time.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.54,0:10:43.05,Default,Sug,0,0,0,,So we decided to form the choir club!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.40,0:10:46.10,Default,Sug,0,0,0,,She may not be able to play violin, but she can sing!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.10,0:10:49.13,Default,Sug,0,0,0,,She's really great at it, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.29,0:10:53.50,Default,Sug,0,0,0,,Please! Don't get in Rie-chan's way!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.38,0:10:55.96,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,Um…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.96,0:10:58.00,Sun,Sun,0,0,0,,You don't have to listen to someone like her!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.34,0:11:03.84,Sun,Sun,0,0,0,,Someone who tries to draw sympathy out of others like that is a cheater!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.25,0:11:08.85,Sun,Sun,0,0,0,,It's despicable for someone to expect\Nspecial treatment due to a handicap like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.37,0:11:12.50,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Sunohara…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.77,0:11:15.15,Sun,Sun,0,0,0,,A handicap like that…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.56,0:11:24.74,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,I can't get in Nishina-san's way.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.44,0:11:27.48,Sun,Sun,0,0,0,,You haven't done anything wrong, Nagisa-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.48,0:11:29.97,Sun,Sun,0,0,0,,Forget the things she said!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.97,0:11:30.75,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,But…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.40,0:11:33.25,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,…I've already heard them.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.75,0:11:40.80,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,The choir club is seriously trying\Nto create music, but the drama club is…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.31,0:11:46.26,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,Sugisaka-san. I'll give up on the drama club.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.26,0:11:47.98,Default,Sug,0,0,0,,Furukawa-san…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.98,0:11:52.52,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,So please create a wonderful choir club with Nishina-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.35,0:11:55.64,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Sunohara!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.55,0:12:03.54,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Sunohara is the same as me.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.15,0:12:08.66,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,He joined a club as part of the school's sports recruitment, and ended up having to quit.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.66,0:12:10.51,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,Sunohara-san did?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.51,0:12:12.30,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,He was on the soccer team.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.30,0:12:16.48,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,But he clashed with an upperclassman, got in a fight, and had to quit.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.02,0:12:18.71,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,The rest is the same story as mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.71,0:12:21.65,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Nothing to do and just wasting every day away.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.99,0:12:23.90,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,I see…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.90,0:12:28.24,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,He's the same in the sense that he had to give up on a dream midway through.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.79,0:12:32.16,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,That's why he can't forgive others taking advantage of that handicap.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.20,0:12:37.24,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Hey, was this really the best choice?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.37,0:12:42.59,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,Okazaki-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.59,0:12:43.52,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.52,0:12:48.06,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,It was very fun to work hard with you up until now.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.80,0:12:55.85,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,I couldn't reestablish the drama club,\Nbut I found many more important things.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.52,0:12:59.35,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,I was able to become close with Okazaki-san…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.70,0:13:04.01,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,…and with Kyou-chan, Ryou-chan,\NKotomi-chan, and Sunohara-san, as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.00,0:13:11.09,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,It's thanks to you that even I was able to work this hard.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.09,0:13:13.58,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,I haven't done anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.58,0:13:15.52,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,That's not true.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.84,0:13:17.62,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,It's you who's become strong.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.12,0:13:20.59,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,A lot stronger than that day\Nyou stood at the bottom of the hill.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.33,0:13:25.00,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Even if you're a clumsy crybaby, you worked hard to come this far.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.00,0:13:26.99,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,That's why you became strong.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.99,0:13:31.76,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,If you weren't with me,\NI wouldn't have been able to do anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.73,0:13:38.10,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,I'm sorry…{ep 14}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.45,0:13:40.23,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,I didn't mean to cry…{ep 14}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.77,0:13:41.80,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Nagisa…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.49,0:13:55.30,Kyo,Kyo,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.56,0:13:57.25,Kyo,Kyo,0,0,0,,I heard from Youhei!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.25,0:14:01.67,Kyo,Kyo,0,0,0,,You gave in to the choir member's tears and gave Koumura-sensei to them?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.67,0:14:03.91,Kyo,Kyo,0,0,0,,How can you be like that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.91,0:14:07.39,Kyo,Kyo,0,0,0,,If you're always so considerate of others, you'll never realize your dreams!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.22,0:14:12.58,Sun,Sun,0,0,0,,I don't like this either.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.58,0:14:17.53,Sun,Sun,0,0,0,,If Nagisa-chan isn't going to do it,\Nthen I'll go destroy the choir with force.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.53,0:14:19.26,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,That's one thing you shouldn't do.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.26,0:14:21.35,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,It'll only make Nagisa more sad.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.96,0:14:23.63,Sun,Sun,0,0,0,,I don't like this at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.63,0:14:26.31,Sun,Sun,0,0,0,,Okazaki, let's go fool around somewhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.31,0:14:30.86,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,But I just withdrew from my account the other day, so I'm broke.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.83,0:14:34.45,Yuk,Yuk,0,0,0,,Welcome, Okazaki-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.80,0:14:37.20,Sun,Sun,0,0,0,,What is going on here?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.74,0:14:41.20,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,A place where you can drink good coffee for free and can kill time, as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.20,0:14:42.74,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Not bad, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.74,0:14:45.63,Yuk,Yuk,0,0,0,,My name is Miyazawa Yukine.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.63,0:14:49.42,Yuk,Yuk,0,0,0,,I'm in charge of the key to this reference room.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.31,0:14:51.93,Sun,Sun,0,0,0,,Is there a meaning to that? {ep 14}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.52,0:14:55.77,Sun,Sun,0,0,0,,All the books here are books no one reads, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.77,0:14:57.29,Yuk,Yuk,0,0,0,,That's why it's great.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.29,0:14:59.64,Yuk,Yuk,0,0,0,,All the strange books are collected here.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.06,0:15:02.54,Yuk,Yuk,0,0,0,,For example, this.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.54,0:15:04.70,Yuk,Yuk,0,0,0,,It's fortune telling using astrological signs.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.70,0:15:06.72,Yuk,Yuk,0,0,0,,Sunohara-san, what's your sign?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.96,0:15:10.11,Yuk,Yuk,0,0,0,,Your constellation says…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.11,0:15:15.22,Sun,Sun,0,0,0,,If anything, I'd like to know how to get the advisor back from the choir.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.22,0:15:17.52,Yuk,Yuk,0,0,0,,Your lucky color is orange.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.52,0:15:19.79,Yuk,Yuk,0,0,0,,Your lucky word is basketball.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.37,0:15:21.86,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Basketball… {ep 14}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.86,0:15:24.62,Sun,Sun,0,0,0,,Between the two of us, that'd be your field. {ep 14}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.62,0:15:27.38,Yuk,Yuk,0,0,0,,You're very considerate of your friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.38,0:15:32.50,Yuk,Yuk,0,0,0,,By showing that you sincerely care, those around you will be touched.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.50,0:15:37.11,Yuk,Yuk,0,0,0,,How you challenge what seems impossible will move others' hearts.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.50,0:15:39.82,Sun,Sun,0,0,0,,Challenge the impossible…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.82,0:15:41.51,Sun,Sun,0,0,0,,Basketball…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.68,0:15:43.68,Sun,Sun,0,0,0,,That's it!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.15,0:15:45.28,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Hey, Sunohara!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.28,0:15:46.65,Sun,Sun,0,0,0,,Later, Okazaki!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.90,0:15:50.20,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,What did that idiot think of?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.37,0:15:51.36,Tom,Tom,0,0,0,,No matter how many times you come,\Nmy answer will be the same.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.36,0:15:53.03,Default,Girl,0,0,0,,Don't say that, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.03,0:15:56.27,Default,Girl,0,0,0,,Please, Sakagami-san. Join the women's judo club.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.27,0:15:59.00,Default,Guy,0,0,0,,As the men's judo club president, I beg of you, as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.00,0:16:02.20,Default,Guy,0,0,0,,If you join, the women's team would instantly become championship contenders.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.20,0:16:04.65,Tom,Tom,0,0,0,,I've told you many times that I have no intention of joining.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.65,0:16:07.24,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,You're popular as always, Tomoyo.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.24,0:16:09.09,Tom,Tom,0,0,0,,Okazaki, help me.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.09,0:16:10.13,Tom,Tom,0,0,0,,They're so persistant.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.07,0:16:10.13,Default-alt,Girl,0,0,0,,Just visiting is fine to start.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.13,0:16:12.08,Default,Guy,0,0,0,,Just today!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.08,0:16:13.50,Default,Girl,0,0,0,,Please, Sakagami-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.95,0:16:15.06,Tom,Tom,0,0,0,,I have a mission!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.95,0:16:16.47,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,You—
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.91,0:16:21.70,Fuk,Fuk,0,0,0,,Fuuko is here!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.73,0:16:30.44,Fuk,Fuk,0,0,0,,Sakagami-san came to Onee-chan's wedding.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.44,0:16:32.86,Fuk,Fuk,0,0,0,,It is now Fuuko's turn to be of her aid.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.86,0:16:38.78,Fuk,Fuk,0,0,0,,Looks like the time to show Fuuko's ultimate move that wipes out any enemies, Starfish Heat!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.07,0:16:44.63,Fuk,Fuk,0,0,0,,But you two participated in the wedding, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.94,0:16:50.12,Fuk,Fuk,0,0,0,,Fuuko can't take either side.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.12,0:16:52.57,Fuk,Fuk,0,0,0,,Fuuko will show up on another occasion.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.19,0:16:54.41,Fuk,Fuk,0,0,0,,Until then.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.92,0:16:56.57,Tom,Tom,0,0,0,,What was that about?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.57,0:16:57.99,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,No, don't ask me.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.99,0:17:00.07,Default,Girl,0,0,0,,Anyway, please come to the dojo.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.07,0:17:01.86,Default,Guy,0,0,0,,If you do, I'm sure your mind will change.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.86,0:17:03.61,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Why don't you guys stop already?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.61,0:17:04.89,Default,Guy,0,0,0,,Who are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.77,0:17:08.62,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Let's go, Tomoyo.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.62,0:17:09.87,Tom,Tom,0,0,0,,Y-Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.14,0:17:15.65,Tom,Tom,0,0,0,,I was amazed. You can be dependable when the situation requires you to be.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.65,0:17:18.05,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,It wasn't anything that grand.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.05,0:17:20.40,Tom,Tom,0,0,0,,You were facing the judo club's captains.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.40,0:17:22.70,Tom,Tom,0,0,0,,Not just one, but from both\Nthe men's and women's teams.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.70,0:17:24.45,Tom,Tom,0,0,0,,Were you not afraid?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.45,0:17:26.08,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,I'm used to being hated,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.08,0:17:27.18,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,so don't worry about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.61,0:17:31.16,Tom,Tom,0,0,0,,Given how things were going,\NI might have been forced into the club.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.50,0:17:36.51,Tom,Tom,0,0,0,,I'm not interested in judo, and soon I'll be busy with the student council president election.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.70,0:17:44.01,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,If someone like you were president,\Nreestablishing the drama club could have been easier.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.77,0:17:46.59,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.59,0:17:49.44,Tom,Tom,0,0,0,,I was thinking that you're actually a pretty decent guy.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.19,0:17:59.96,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,Then you didn't see Sunohara-san last night?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.96,0:18:03.03,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Yeah, he didn't come home until pretty late.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.91,0:18:07.04,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,I don't have a clue where and what he was doing.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.08,0:18:12.27,Sun,Sun,0,0,0,,I've been waiting.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.13,0:18:14.88,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,A match against the basketball team?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.88,0:18:18.22,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Hold on! Where did this come from?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.22,0:18:20.19,Sun,Sun,0,0,0,,Remember what Yukine-chan said yesterday?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.19,0:18:23.61,Sun,Sun,0,0,0,,I can emotionally touch those\Naround me by working fanatically.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.61,0:18:26.14,Sun,Sun,0,0,0,,And the lucky word is basketball.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.14,0:18:30.21,Sun,Sun,0,0,0,,In other words, if we have a match against the basketball team and win, {Combine in 16.9}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.21,0:18:33.54,Sun,Sun,0,0,0,,we can get those choir girls to understand my point.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.54,0:18:36.10,Sun,Sun,0,0,0,,Those handicaps don't mean anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.10,0:18:41.21,Sun,Sun,0,0,0,,Sugisaka and Nishina will be so moved that they will give us the advisor.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.88,0:18:47.45,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,You really think a shounen manga-like plot like that would really work?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.45,0:18:49.74,Sun,Sun,0,0,0,,I know you can't shoot.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.74,0:18:51.18,Sun,Sun,0,0,0,,So be the point guard.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.18,0:18:52.20,Sun,Sun,0,0,0,,Let's do this!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.20,0:18:53.72,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,I can't go along with this.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.72,0:18:54.79,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Let's go, Nagisa.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.73,0:18:57.67,Sun,Sun,0,0,0,,Hey, hold on Okazaki!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.06,0:19:02.39,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,Was it all right to leave Sunohara-san behind?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.39,0:19:04.82,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,He's just getting excited by himself.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.82,0:19:05.85,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Don't let it bother you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.85,0:19:09.35,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,But he's doing this for me…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.72,0:19:14.31,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Was there any case where he did anything for someone else?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.31,0:19:15.36,Sun,Sun,0,0,0,,Okazaki!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.36,0:19:16.38,Sun,Sun,0,0,0,,Let's play basketball!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.35,0:19:18.65,Sun,Sun,0,0,0,,Hey, Okazaki.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.65,0:19:19.59,Sun,Sun,0,0,0,,Let's play basketball!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.59,0:19:20.40,Sun,Sun,0,0,0,,Okazaki!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.40,0:19:21.17,Sun,Sun,0,0,0,,Let's play basketball.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.17,0:19:22.64,Sun,Sun,0,0,0,,Hey, come on.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.05,0:19:26.87,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Sensei. Sunohara-kun is disturbing my studies.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.80,0:19:31.22,Sun,Sun,0,0,0,,Hold up, Okazaki!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.14,0:19:34.26,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,Okazaki-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.26,0:19:35.27,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,Shall we go to the club room—
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.27,0:19:35.84,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Run!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.21,0:19:41.46,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,I'm sure he won't come this far.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.78,0:19:46.18,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,Wouldn't Sunohara-san be looking for you?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.18,0:19:47.96,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,It's fine. Forget about him.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.96,0:19:48.87,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,But…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.72,0:19:52.85,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Okay, I'll tell the truth. {ep 14}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.85,0:19:53.60,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,What? {ep 14}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.60,0:19:57.36,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Basketball practice is just an excuse to be with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.36,0:19:58.29,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,An excuse?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.29,0:19:59.07,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.40,0:20:01.63,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,He actually likes me.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.63,0:20:02.87,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,He loves me.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.87,0:20:03.95,Sun,Sun,0,0,0,,Okazaki.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.95,0:20:09.52,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,I've left him alone for a while, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.52,0:20:12.94,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,So the loneliness has built up within him\Nand is making him do this.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.94,0:20:15.18,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,If you think about it, he's an unfortunate guy.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.48,0:20:19.50,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,But, if so, shouldn't you seriously face him?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.50,0:20:23.05,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Unfortunately, I can't love men.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.05,0:20:27.89,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,So it's better for him to give up on me sooner rather than later.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.89,0:20:29.22,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,I see…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.22,0:20:32.06,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,You really are a kind person.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.06,0:20:33.77,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,As long as you understand me.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.30,0:20:37.19,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,He's here!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.44,0:20:39.94,Sun,Sun,0,0,0,,I finally caught up.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.94,0:20:42.49,Sun,Sun,0,0,0,,Why did you run away, Okazaki?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.49,0:20:43.33,Sun,Sun,0,0,0,,You're being so unfriendly.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.90,0:20:45.94,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,Um… well…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.32,0:20:49.56,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,Okazaki-san isn't appreciating it,\Nso I don't think you should.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.56,0:20:50.46,Sun,Sun,0,0,0,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.46,0:20:53.18,Sun,Sun,0,0,0,,You know Okazaki and I get along well.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.18,0:20:58.29,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,You can't! Even if you're close to each other, there are lines that you can't cross!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.29,0:21:00.95,Sun,Sun,0,0,0,,I need Okazaki no matter what!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.95,0:21:03.30,Sun,Sun,0,0,0,,It must be him!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.30,0:21:04.52,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,You can't!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.52,0:21:05.67,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,Since…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.24,0:21:09.26,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,Since Okazaki-san is my boyfriend!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.93,0:21:11.01,Default,2,0,0,0,,Eh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.01,0:21:16.31,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,So I can't give Okazaki-san to you!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.31,0:21:18.38,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Oh, I see. She's trying to protect me.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.38,0:21:19.94,Sun,Sun,0,0,0,,You two…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.94,0:21:21.20,Sun,Sun,0,0,0,,Since when…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.75,0:21:25.40,Sun,Sun,0,0,0,,You idiots!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.00,0:21:33.32,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.40,0:21:40.74,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,I'm sorry! I felt that I had to protect you,\Nso without thinking I shouted out a complete lie.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.17,0:21:43.42,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Ah, no. Um…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.34,0:21:46.31,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Thanks. It made me happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.23,0:21:54.14,Default,Mei,0,0,0,,Excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.61,0:21:58.52,Default,Mei,0,0,0,,Was the person who just ran by Sunohara Youhei?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.52,0:21:59.77,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,And you are?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.02,0:22:03.02,Default,Mei,0,0,0,,His younger sister,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.02,0:22:05.27,Default,Mei,0,0,0,,Sunohara Mei.
