Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.39,0:23:43.05,Tom,Tom,0,0,0,,Do you have someone you're dating right now?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.05,0:23:43.93,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,No, I don't!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.93,0:23:45.56,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,And why are you even asking this?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.56,0:23:48.36,Kyo,Kyo,0,0,0,,Tomoya, you just said something interesting, didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.36,0:23:50.72,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,The interesting ones were Sunohara and Tomoyo.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.72,0:23:53.18,Kyo,Kyo,0,0,0,,That's not what I mean.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.18,0:23:55.47,Kyo,Kyo,0,0,0,,You said you're not dating anyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.47,0:23:57.88,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Yeah, so what?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.88,0:24:01.14,Kyo,Kyo,0,0,0,,I don't know. I wonder what it means.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.14,0:24:02.53,Sun,Sun,0,0,0,,Nagisa-chan and Okazaki?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.53,0:24:04.00,Sun,Sun,0,0,0,,What are you two doing in my room?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.91,0:24:05.93,Sun,Sun,0,0,0,,You weren't possibly going to…
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.93,0:24:07.65,Sun,Sun,0,0,0,,…make this your nest of love?!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.65,0:24:09.54,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,No! No!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.54,0:24:11.73,Default,,0,0,0,,
